# ImageAnalysisInteraction.SubjectUnavailable

**Enumeration**

Error conditions that can occur during subject analysis.

## Declaration

```swift
enum SubjectUnavailable
```

## Overview

This enumeration contains a failure [doc://com.apple.VisionKit/documentation/VisionKit/ImageAnalysisInteraction/SubjectUnavailable/imageUnavailable] that can occur when the [doc://com.apple.VisionKit/documentation/VisionKit/ImageAnalysisInteraction/Subject] property [doc://com.apple.VisionKit/documentation/VisionKit/ImageAnalysisInteraction/Subject/image] fails to produce a result.

## Identifying an error cause

- **ImageAnalysisInteraction.SubjectUnavailable.imageUnavailable**: An error that indicates the subject fails to produce an image.

## Conforms To

- Copyable
- Equatable
- Error
- Hashable
- Sendable
- SendableMetatype
